Cell["Elastodynamic Green\[CloseCurlyQuote]s Tensor \[Dash] 2D FFT \
Verification", "Title",ExpressionUUID->"608af17c-b266-486a-a845-984fef93fc74"],

Cell["\<\
Mathematica translation of greens_fft_cli.py
T.M. Nestor, ANU Thesis\
